reviews.comment: Great chair, very sturdy. Has a few scratches as described, but that adds to the vintage charm.
The pan set is in excellent condition, practically new. A great deal!
Perfect yoga mat, and the seller was very friendly. Highly recommend.
It's a decent chair for the price, but a bit wobbly. Might need some minor repairs.
